.head 8 -  ! GF 03/10/03 Changed this next statement to show unapplied cash that is associated with outstanding deposits as I have a case where over
$3000 is not showing to be used in teh transaction screen. To reverse this uncomment following statement
.head 8 -  Set sBuildWhere = ' WHERE Cust_No = :frmTransaction.dfCustNo AND Fully_Applied_Flag = \'N\' '
.head 8 -  ! Set sBuildWhere = ' WHERE Cust_No = :frmTransaction.dfCustNo AND Fully_Applied_Flag = \'N\' 
AND RCPT_SYSDATETIME NOT IN (SELECT RCPT_SYSDATETIME FROM OUTSTAND_DEPOSIT WHERE
CUST_NO = :frmTransaction.dfCustNo )'
.head 8 -  ! GF that was the statement
