.head 8 +  If NOT SalIsNull( colUserViewDepositSysDT )
.head 9 -  ! the bollow check is need over the GetUniqueCurrentSysDT( ) because SalDateSecond( ) only returns
whole seconds between 0-59 and GetUniqueCurrentSysDT( ) gives unique in microseconds
.head 9 -  Set dtTmp = SalDateConstruct( SalDateYear( colUserViewDepositSysDT ), SalDateMonth( colUserViewDepositSysDT ), SalDateDay( colUserViewDepositSysDT ), SalDateHour( dtTmp ), SalDateMinute( 
